g.text: Norway’s legal biofuel minimum requirement for road transport

text.tspan: So-called 'advanced' biofuels have a separate minimum requirement, and from
late 2018 these count for double to encourage their supply.
Advanced biofuels are those that are unlikely to lead indirectly to
deforestation or compete with food production.
